      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DREAMERS NEVER DIE (2) resumed in good order over 1200m a fortnight ago, closing off nicely to be 2.4L off the winner. Fiore hops back aboard today last time she was on board, he won by 3.9L. Can land in a handy position and with the fresh run under his belt, he'll be hard to fend off. FAVAIOS (4) is racing well recently, finishing 0.9L off the winner most recently when a $26 chance over 1200m. Up in trip today shouldn't be an issue and if he can run up to his recent effort, he'll be hard to hold out. HIGH PRECISION (8) rates highly in this field on her recent form, flying home last start when getting well back from the draw. Riordan's claim helps and she won't be far away. THE LIONS' GATE (5) won't be far away on recent form. EEVALINA (3) can improve on the fresh run.",
